263
00:25:45,210 --> 00:25:46,669
<i>Airborne?</i>

264
00:25:49,423 --> 00:25:51,174
<i>He was 38 years old.</i>

265
00:25:53,135 --> 00:25:55,345
<i>Why the fuck would he do that?</i>

266
00:25:57,640 --> 00:26:00,934
