273
00:26:16,784 --> 00:26:18,785
Charlie don't never see them
or hear them, man.

274
00:26:18,869 --> 00:26:21,079
- There they are.
- Concussion will suck the air

275
00:26:21,163 --> 00:26:22,538
out of your damn lungs.

276
00:26:23,123 --> 00:26:26,209
- Something terrible is gonna happen.
