287
00:27:19,555 --> 00:27:23,099
<i>that had cashed in its horses for choppers</i>
<i>and gone tear-assing around Nam</i>

288
00:27:23,183 --> 00:27:25,018
<i>looking for the shit.</i>

289
00:27:25,519 --> 00:27:29,355
<i>They'd given Charlie a few surprises</i>
<i>in their time here.</i>

290
00:27:30,274 --> 00:27:33,901
